Install:
1. Copy bookmarklet text below and drag to bookmark bar.
2. Change YOURNAME to your kindle email account.
3. Add "kindle@eumacro.csie.org" to your approved email list at https://www.amazon.com/gp/digital/fiona/manage?ie=UTF8&*Version*=1&*entries*=0&#pdocSettings
4. Select text on any page and click the bookmarklet just created on bookmark bar.

--------Begin bookmarklet--------
javascript:void(window.open('http://eumacro.csie.org/kindle/?to=YOURNAME@free.kindle.com&body='+encodeURIComponent(window.getSelection())));
--------End of bookmarklet-------

